'''阿德伯里湖'''是位于[[牛津郡|牛津郡]][[阿德伯里|阿德伯里]]的当地自然保护区，占地{{convert|1.8|ha|acre|abbr=off}}，由阿德伯里教区议会拥有管辖。<ref name=LNR>{{cite web |url=https://designatedsites.naturalengland.org.uk/SiteLNRDetail.aspx?SiteCode=L1481439&SiteName=&countyCode=34&responsiblePerson=&SeaArea=&IFCAArea= |title=Adderbury Lakes |series=Local Nature Reserves |publisher=Natural England |accessdate=8 April 2020 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922123728/https://designatedsites.naturalengland.org.uk/SiteLNRDetail.aspx?SiteCode=L1481439&SiteName=&countyCode=34&responsiblePerson=&SeaArea=&IFCAArea= |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=LNRmap>{{cite web|url= https://magic.defra.gov.uk/MagicMap.aspx?startTopic=Designations&activelayer=lnrIndex&query=Ref_CODE%3D%271481439%27|title= Map of Adderbury Lakes|series= Local Nature Reserves|publisher= Natural England|accessdate= 8  April 2020|archive-date= 2020-10-17|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201017093811/https://magic.defra.gov.uk/MagicMap.aspx?startTopic=Designations&activelayer=lnrIndex&query=Ref_CODE%3D%271481439%27|dead-url= no}}</ref>

阿德伯里湖在1768年由[[万能布朗|万能布朗]]创建，并成为了阿德伯里屋的一部分。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.parksandgardens.org/places/adderbury-house|title=Adderbury House|publisher=Parks & Gardens|accessdate=8  April 2020|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017163550/https://www.parksandgardens.org/places/adderbury-house|dead-url=no}}</ref>该保护区还包括湖泊周围的林地，那里有不同种类的[[野生动物|野生动物]]。<ref name=LNR/>

